HEADWORD: space probe
<hw>space" probe</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>an unmanned rocket carrying
instruments to explore objects or conditions in outer space; -- used
mostly for vehicles travelling beyond the earth's gravitational field,
rather than in orbital or suborbital flight.</def>⟦br⟧
